"{\"uid\": \"mensxp.com-fashion-trends-166822-mongolia-paris-2024-olympic-uniform-a-masterclass-in-simple-yet-majestic-fashion.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Specialty:Journalism  Qualification:PG Diploma Journalismfrom IIMC  Experience:6Years  TheParis 2024 Olympicsare around the corner, where thousands of world-class athletes will be competing to bring glory to their nation.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 62, \"end\": 66, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IIMC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Continuing with the tradition, the Paris Olympics 2024 will also begin with a grand opening ceremony, withsportspersons from across the globeintroducing themselves to the world while marching under their country's flag.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Billions of spectators will tune in from different parts of the globe to watch their respective nations taking centre stage at the grand opening ceremony in the French capital, but all eyes will be on Team Mongolia.\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9993407327485858, \"rank\": 0.0006580356627797641, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.380437480892058e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Mongolia's new uniform designed for the opening ceremony of the 2024 Paris Olympics has set a new benchmark in simple yet majestic fashion.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.380437480892058e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Designed by the extremely talented designer sisters Michel and Amazonka, these outfits blends Mongolia's rich culture with modern aesthetics, demonstrating how minimalistic fashion can capture everyone's imagination.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"score\": 0.9999999991478035, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amazonka\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.380437480892058e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Interestingly, it wasn't their first attempt.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You see, creating magic takes time!\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The talented sisters had previously designed Team Mongolia's uniforms in the previous two editions -2020 Tokyo Olympicsand 2022 Beijing Winter Games, but those attires did not make such noise.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.380437480892058e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, they were not even supposed to design the uniforms.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Mongolian National Olympic Committee (MNOC) had given the contract to another company.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mongolian National Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, that company backed off from the deal for some reason in February, leaving the governing body in a spot of bother.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since Michel & Amazonka had already delivered similar projects in the past, the MNOC reached out to them, offering only three months to conceptualise and design the uniform.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite time being their biggest enemy, the designer duo was able to create a beautiful dress, a masterclass in simple yet majestic fashion that would go down in the annals of Olympic history.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Table of Contents    Mongolia might not be a sporting powerhouse but the country boasts a rich history and culture.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of looking outside for inspiration, the designers drew their inspiration from theNaadam Festival,which is considered their Olympics andtakes place in July every year.\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During this festival, people compete in various competitions wearing similar outfits.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic uniform is inspired by Mongolian deels which have been parts of their part of their culture for centuries.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2362, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.7600760621670413, \"rank\": 0.3151745826382451, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The designers have added some modern design elements to make their national athletes stand out from the rest.\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of complicating things, the designers chose a simple yet powerful design.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The uniforms are sharp, and precise, with boxy vests and embroidered collars.\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This design pattern avoids overcomplication, resulting in a timeless elegance that appeals to both classic and modern sensibilities.\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The uniform is a perfect amalgamation of simplicity and modernity.\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The designers have paid great attention to detail, especially in the embroidery.\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They deliberately designed every aspect of the costume to communicate symbolism.\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every little needlework has a deep underlying meaning.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 'Nine White Banner' represents fresh starts, while the mountains reflect the athletes' journey and hard work.\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The use of golden thread in the embroidery signifies their desire to win gold medals.\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This meticulous integration of symbols adds meaning to the design, transforming the uniforms into a story about the Mongolian spirit and ambition.\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3452, \"end\": 3461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.7600760621670413, \"rank\": 0.3151745826382451, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These intricate details offer a touch of refinement without dominating the design.\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At a time when flashy colours have become the norm, the designers made the practical needs of their athletes their topmost priority.\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of choosing extravagant colours, they picked light colours like white and grey, making the fabric more breathable inhot weather in Paris.\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3841, \"end\": 3846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1383024715097073e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apart from being cool (pun intended) the choice of colours conveys a sense of tranquillity and sophistication.\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, the fabrics used are lightweight and comfortable, making sure that the athletes move freely without any discomfort throughout the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 4113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Specialty:Journalism  Qualification:PG Diploma Journalismfrom IIMC  Experience:6Years\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4177, \"end\": 4181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IIMC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\"}]}]}"